net.maidsafe.api

Class Session

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.maidsafe.api.Session
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Client

    public class Session
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds a client session with the network. This is the primary interface to interact with the network. As such it provides all API-Providers connected through this session.
